<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/61165593/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/61165593/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">看看热闹</span>
